text: Nokho, zinenhlobo ehlukile yobuhle nokukhanga phakathi nobusika, ngamagquma amanithi athola iqhwa elanele nanikeza okokuzijabulisa okunjengokushushuluza eqhweni noma ukuntweza ngoqembe eqhweni.
Lawa mahhotela bekuyilapho abacebile nabadumile bangaleyo nkathi ababehlala khona, futhi kaningi ayenokuhla okuphambili nezenzakalo zasebusuku.

Ekuqaleni kwempi yahamba kakhulu ngaphezu kolwandle, kodwa njengoba ireda yaqala ukukhula nokucacisa okwengeziwe, imikhumbi yangaphansi komhlaba yaphoqelelwa ukuba ihambe ngaphansi kwamanzi ukuze ingabonwa.
Njengoba ulwazi lwaseGrisi lwaluncipha, iNtshonalanga yazithola isuka ezimpandeni zayo zefilosofi nesayensi zobuGriki.

Ama-athomu mancane kakhulu ngendlela emangazayo kangangokuba ama-trillion awo angangena ku ngqi ekugcineni kwalomusho.

Izivakashi ezinesikhathi esilinganiselwe zingenza kahle ukuchitha isikhathi sazo kwenye indawo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, phawula ukuthi iphunga libiza amabhere kanye nezinye izilwane zasendle, ngakho gwema ukuphatha noma ukupheka ukudla okunephunga futhi ugcine ikamu lihlanzekile.
Ukubhukha kusenesikhathi kunikeza isihambi ukuthula kwengqondo kokuthi sizoba nendawo yokulala kuyo lapho sifika endaweni esiya kuyo.

Umgwaqo obanzi okakwe izihlahla, izakhiwe ezinezingilazi ezinkulu kanye nendawo nezikhungo zezitolo zinophahla olungokwesiko olubomvu, imakethe yangekhulu lama-18 leminyaka, kanye namathempeli namasonto, nakuba idolobha linomoya omningi weYurophu yaseMedithera kunaseTheki engokwesiko.
Kuzo zonke izimo, kumelwe ubhukhe ngefoni ngokuqondile nenkampani yezindiza.
